# Translated with gpt-4.1-mini
#: ../main_window.rst:41
msgid ""
"This toolbar contains buttons used for snapping, inserting markers, slicing "
"razor, jumping between markers, and centering the timeline on the playhead. "
"See :ref:`timeline_toolbar_ref`."
